{
  "schema_version": "1.1",
  "category": "concurrency",
  "description": "Swift concurrency and async patterns mapped to ArkTS implementation patterns. These are not platform capabilities and do not enter feature_adaptation.",
  "capabilities": [
    {
      "id": "concurrency.task_group",
      "category": "concurrency",
      "ios": {
        "frameworks": [
          "Swift"
        ],
        "apis": [
          "withTaskGroup",
          "TaskGroup",
          "withThrowingTaskGroup"
        ],
        "entitlements": [],
        "permissions": []
      },
      "harmony": {
        "kit": "ArkTS",
        "api_area": "Promise.all / Promise.allSettled",
        "target_boundary": "services/*"
      },
      "strategy": "api_replacement",
      "permission": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "manifest": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "risk_level": "medium",
      "implementation_notes": [
        "Swift withTaskGroup → ArkTS Promise.all 并发执行",
        "如果 ios-spec.json.functions concurrency_detail 含 maxConcurrency=N，则按 N 个一组分批 Promise.all，否则一次性全部并发",
        "禁止简化为串行 for 循环"
      ],
      "fallback": "无。并发是性能关键路径，不允许退化。"
    },
    {
      "id": "concurrency.async_let",
      "category": "concurrency",
      "ios": {
        "frameworks": [
          "Swift"
        ],
        "apis": [
          "async let"
        ],
        "entitlements": [],
        "permissions": []
      },
      "harmony": {
        "kit": "ArkTS",
        "api_area": "Promise.all",
        "target_boundary": "services/*"
      },
      "strategy": "native_equivalent",
      "permission": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "manifest": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "risk_level": "low",
      "implementation_notes": [
        "Swift async let a = fetchA(); async let b = fetchB(); return await (a, b)",
        "→ ArkTS const [a, b] = await Promise.all([fetchA(), fetchB()])",
        "多个 async let 并发发起 → 合并为一个 Promise.all"
      ],
      "fallback": "无。"
    },
    {
      "id": "concurrency.callback",
      "category": "concurrency",
      "ios": {
        "frameworks": [
          "Foundation"
        ],
        "apis": [
          "completion handler",
          "delegate pattern"
        ],
        "entitlements": [],
        "permissions": []
      },
      "harmony": {
        "kit": "ArkTS",
        "api_area": "Promise / async-await wrapper",
        "target_boundary": "services/*"
      },
      "strategy": "api_replacement",
      "permission": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "manifest": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "risk_level": "low",
      "implementation_notes": [
        "iOS callback/completion handler → ArkTS Promise 封装",
        "iOS delegate pattern → ArkTS 回调函数或事件回调",
        "保持异步调用链的清晰度，不要嵌套回调"
      ],
      "fallback": "无。"
    },
    {
      "id": "concurrency.async_await",
      "category": "concurrency",
      "ios": {
        "frameworks": [
          "Swift"
        ],
