      },
      "harmony": {
        "kit": "ArkTS",
        "api_area": "TaskPool / Worker / Promise",
        "target_boundary": "services/*"
      },
      "strategy": "api_replacement",
      "permission": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "manifest": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "risk_level": "medium",
      "implementation_notes": [
        "DispatchQueue.global().async { } → TaskPool.execute 或 new Promise",
        "DispatchGroup.wait() → Promise.all + 计数器",
        "DispatchSemaphore → 自定义计数锁或串行化队列"
      ],
      "fallback": "用 Promise 串行执行"
    },
    {
      "id": "concurrency.actor",
      "category": "concurrency",
      "ios": {
        "frameworks": [
          "Swift"
        ],
        "apis": [
          "actor",
          "isolated",
          "nonisolated",
          "@GlobalActor"
        ],
        "entitlements": [],
        "permissions": []
      },
      "harmony": {
        "kit": "ArkTS",
        "api_area": "class + 单实例序列化",
        "target_boundary": "services/*, stores/*"
      },
      "strategy": "api_replacement",
      "permission": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "manifest": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "risk_level": "medium",
      "implementation_notes": [
        "Swift actor → 普通 class，方法加 async 标记",
        "Actor 的数据隔离 → 用单例 + Promise 串行化保证线程安全",
        "如果有 MainActor → 确保在 UI 线程执行（ArkUI 默认在 UI 线程）"
      ],
      "fallback": "无。"
    },
    {
      "id": "concurrency.async_stream",
      "category": "concurrency",
      "ios": {
        "frameworks": [
          "Swift"
        ],
        "apis": [
          "AsyncStream",
          "AsyncSequence",
          "AsyncThrowingStream"
        ],
        "entitlements": [],
        "permissions": []
      },
      "harmony": {
        "kit": "ArkTS",
        "api_area": "回调函数 / 事件监听 / 轮询",
        "target_boundary": "services/*"
      },
      "strategy": "api_replacement",
      "permission": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "manifest": {
        "required": false,
        "notes": ""
      },
      "risk_level": "medium",
      "implementation_notes": [
        "AsyncStream { continuation in ... } → 回调函数 + 状态收集",
